    # "Soldier" "Yes, Princess."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_17f931fd:
    # "They honored her command, but Sarah could see she had lost some of their respect."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_3357800a:
    # "Young woman" "Thank you, Princess! Thank you for your mercy!"
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_3e9809ee:
    # "She watched her leap up to his feet and run off, clearly not wishing to risk her good luck by staying here any longer."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_cee93bb2:
    # "The townsfolk murmured somewhat, but Sarah wasn't sure if they approved or if they were upset at missing out on a show."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_7f0eabd2:
    # "She didn't care, either way."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_6a03c3fa:
    # "She knew she had done the right thing. Punishing a young woman over some minor inconvenience was pointless cruelty."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_8d760d89:
    # "That cruelty was at the root of the problem."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_79b8b736:
    # "Everything in this country seemed to operate on one group of people holding another down."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_e9a8b744:
    # "The old houses had rebelled against her family, specifically because they feared that her family would undo even a fraction of that hierarchy."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_284225f5:
    # "They lived and breathed in a world of pointless cruelty and oppression, it was their oxygen."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_8690fbb8:
    # "So what did it make her if she did the same as them? Just the stronger tyrant?"
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_0856e348:
    # "If this war was worth fighting, and Sarah believed that it was, then it was because she and her family offered something better."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_d2b82f1f:
    # "A nation where ordinary people did not have to live in fear of its own soldiers and nobles."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_041d0482:
    # "Sarah knew she could not just be allowed to leave."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_1ce3dfc4:
    # "She had attacked the soldiers, her soldiers, and the girl even proudly admitted it."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_559ef2b1:
    # "If she let her go with no punishment, who knew if the story would spread, and next time one person with a rock would turn out to be a dozen."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_e94e37d7:
    # "No, she concluded. This would end here."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_4c3e5fa8:
    # s "Armsman!"
    s ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_6849e757:
    # "Soldier" "Yes, Princess?"
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_12b1d967:
    # s "Strip this woman, tie her to a pole, and flog her in the square."
    s ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_4e5a9ef8:
    # "Soldier" "As you command!"
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_af82646a:
    # "Sarah could see the attitude of her soldiers shift. They saw her as having their backs."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_497ca32a:
    # "Young woman" "No! Please! You can't do this, you don't have the right!"
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_d0eaed7e:
    # "But Sarah did have the right, as the young woman would soon learn."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_0e748f04:
    # "She struggled again as the soldiers seized her and began tying her to a stake."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_cd500159:
    # "Her rousing speech was now quickly forgotten as the townsfolk saw her beg and cry for a mercy she would not receive."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_37ec133e:
    # "With ease, the soldiers ripped off her cheap clothes and tossed them to the mud, leaving the woman naked and bound to the pillar."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_76fe2265:
    # "A laughter ran through the people watching."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_355f3595:
    # "How quickly they turn on her, Sarah realized."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_2844dd0e:
    # "A soldier approached, whip ready in hand."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_759724c4:
    # "Flogging was not an unknown punishment in the Rosannan military, so the tools as well as the practice were easy to produce."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_c1212642:
    # "However, Sarah knew, for a peasant such a punishment was a rarity."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_da38c369:
    # "And the young woman had quickly gone from revolutionary to a town spectacle."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_77371df9:
    # "The first blow brought the crowd to silence."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_22a92fea:
    # "The snapping of the whip was a violent sound, but the effect on the young woman's body was no less so."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_8bbfd731:
    # "A mist of red blood splashed out and a deep crimson trail as left across her back."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_3181fe5b:
    # "Her body winced and she screamed out, but bound tightly, there was little space for her to move."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_b17c2ee1:
    # "When the second strike of the lash cut across her back, the crowd discovered its amusement again."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_d9aa6696:
    # "In her heart she found the affair horrid, but she forced herself to bear a cold gaze as she looked on."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_db507571:
    # "And she did look on, for she knew she had caused this too."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_96a3919a:
    # "As the whipping continued, the young woman's flailing and cries slowly died out as her body fell to exhaustion."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_5027907f:
    # "The pain mixed with the public humiliation was too much, and she soon fainted."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_766798a2:
    # "When the last whip struck her body, she did not even so much as move or make a sound."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_23e0b4bf:
    # "Flogging was cruel business, but flogging someone who could not even feel or cry out was senseless."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_59dbcf66:
    # "The message had been made."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_f0d1264f:
    # s "Take her down and mend her wounds."
    s ""

