    # "Soldier" "At once, my princess!"
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_a0196a9c:
    # "Moving as one, the soldiers easily untied the young woman and carefully placed her on a stretcher, applying bandages to the very wounds they had just caused."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_ada2270f:
    # "She would heal, Sarah knew."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_8e83f87a:
    # "It would take weeks before the pain in her back had fully faded, and the scars would probably last a lifetime, but she would survive this injury."
