translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_621f6ccc:
    # "But then again, that had been the point. To forever snuff out any hint of resistance."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_fa76683a:
    # "Because it was resistance and rebellion that had brought her to this point. Weakness and a tolerance for weak loyalty."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_f8b492f2:
    # "Sarah told herself, she would unite the country through strength, but she would also root out all hints of disloyalty."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_269a8266:
    # "Peace, both for her family and the ordinary people, could only come by hunting down the traitors."
    ""

translate ru PunishTheYoungMan_a8def705:
    # "It was ugly business, but it was the business of peace."
    ""

